text: Laura Šimenc (born 25 July 1990) is a Slovenian professional racing cyclist. She rides for the No Radunion Vitalogic team. ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian female cyclists Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
